				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\rm{\Delta }}\varphi \,=\,({V}_{F}-{V}_{M})/\beta \approx 0.12$$\end{document}Δφ=(VF−VM)/β≈0.12. Although these results are relevant to phosphorene in FET mode of operation, the fact that both IF and the slope γ are very weakly dependent on drain bias VDS enables a direct comparison with thermionic flux calculated using Eq. (10)
